<div class="container py-5">
  <h1 class="mb-4">About This Project</h1>
  
  <p class="lead">
    This is a personal book review app where you can add, edit, and organize your favorite books.
  </p>
  
  <p>
    It uses <strong>Node.js</strong>, <strong>Express</strong>, <strong>PostgreSQL</strong>, and 
    <strong>EJS templates</strong> to provide a clean way to manage your reading journey.
  </p>

  <div class="mt-4">
    <h3>Features:</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Add and edit book reviews</li>
      <li>Track ISBN and cover images from OpenLibrary</li>
      <li>Rate books and log when you read them</li>
      <li>Sort reviews by rating, date read, or add time</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

